snippet.title: Dome Keeper - 2.4 "Springloaded" | Free Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Get Dome Keeper on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1637320/Dome_Keeper/

Try the free 2.4 Springloaded update for Dome Keeper now! This update includes new gadgets and rework and improvements to existing ones, as well as Prestige Mode season 3! The new gadgets will allow you to make key changes to your Keeper strategies and open up new tactics in the game. Boost your offensive, defensive and information gathering capabilities. The Springloaded Update is available now – try out the changes in your next run!
